command.text: G92 X0 Y0 Z0 C0; openpnp is at 0, grbl must not neccessarily
M42 P0 S0 ; turn off topcamera leds
M42 P1 S0 ; turn off bottomcamera leds
M42 P2 S0 ; turn off vacuum
M42 P3 S0 ; turn off pump
G0 {X:X%.4f} {Y:Y%.4f} {Z:Z%.4f} {Rotation:U%.4f} F{FeedRate:%.0f} ; Send standard Gcode move
M400 ; Wait for moves to complete before returning
